    <h2>
        DISEASE PREDICTION AND FOOD RECOMMENDATION SYSTEM FOR CHRONIC DISEASES
    </h2>

<p>
Presently, people face various chronic diseases due to environmental circumscription and their living habits. So the prediction of chronic disease at an earlier stage becomes a primary task. But the accurate prediction based on symptoms becomes too difficult for the doctor.
Due to the development and advancements in information science and technology, people care more about the healthy diet, it is also becoming a serious issue among people who leading irregular life, long-term unhealthy diet, and other factors to be affected by chronic diseases, such as diabetes, heart disease, cancer and so on. However, most of the diet recommendation systems don't give recommendations for patients who suffer from chronic diseases. The correct prediction of those chronic diseases and recommending healthy foods is the most challenging task. Hence we provide, a system that predicts chronic disease based on the symptoms listed by the patients and recommends traditional Indian foods to reduce the effect of chronic diseases.
